<item>
            <title>[SPR-69] Support for declarative validation (Hibernate Validator, anticipating JSR 303)</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR-69</link>
                <project id="10000" key="SPR">Spring Framework</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Support for defining validation rules on beans via source markup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Support for declarative assignment of PropertyValidationRules to bean properties via Spring-IoC, through a scripting environment such as Groovy/Beanshell, or programatically in plain Java.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
